item.title: CVE-2022-31233|2024-08-03T07:11:39.847Z -- dell -- unisphere%20for%20powermax
item.description: Unisphere for PowerMax versions before 9.2.3.15 contain a privilege escalation vulnerability. An adjacent malicious user may potentially exploit this vulnerability to escalate their privileges and access functionalities they do not have access to.
